name: Secure Logistics
tag_list: secure-logistics, secure-transport, secure-transportation, mail-services, protection, security
overview: Secure Logistics is an Auckland located security firm specialising in secure transportation & logistics of a wide range of products to suit your business needs. They offer currency management, transportation of stock/valuables and mail services. With more than 25 years’ experience in the industry, they are dedicated to tailoring their service to suit your needs and also provide you and your business with the top customer care you deserve.
